{"tid":460192,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺用TOTO既廁所多數無咩伏","createTime":"2017-11-06T12:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T15:31:20.000Z","uid":4363,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7eff2f7b456c134aa425fd88c4d446e6d2d0c7","tid":460192,"uid":4363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:18:20.000Z","msg":"用american standard多數低一兩個檔次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTOTO世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c4b46c7c2b2458c648476d0dad748361c94de2","tid":460192,"uid":80736,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用american standard多數低一兩個檔次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTOTO世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得個頭開得唔錯 我嗰時有幾個角色都覺得有做反角嘅可能性 但我對哩套戲嘅唔好印象大於好印象<br />\n<br />\n1. 吳彥祖嗰part個人觀感有啲隔硬嚟 甚至覺得有啲多餘 個感覺係導演淨係想用香港啲高樓大廈玩吓災難性層層疊 之後就特登安排佢講個計劃名出嚟咁 有啲唔係好知哩part做乜撚咁<br />\n<br />\n2. 父囡情條線打得唔夠入 感動位覺得有啲尷尬<br />\n<br />\n3. 反角個犯事理由太撚唔合理呱 想炸咗全世界之後做個美國總統 做乜鳩？跟住又係俾人捉到就做5分鐘解說點解佢要犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩屌 娘到一個點<br />\n<br />\n4. 雖然知佢係美國電影 但哩套嘅大美國英雄主義 同埋過份歌頌美國嘅情懷 真係有啲嘔心 尤其最後嗰句咩 「因為老子就是美國總統！」WTF<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係馬後炮 但如果個故事變成美國總統真係背後策劃人 為權力而表面做好人 但暗中搵人阻止男主角 整幾條伏線指向其他角色屈鳩佢哋做反角 而女主角同女船長係總統後後嘅間諜咁 可能會好睇啲<br />\n<br />\nsor 可能太認真 但我真心覺得佢曬咗個idea"},{"pid":"cbe64c89a1d91243115923da0f32a8d362c3ea33","tid":460192,"uid":5077,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:38:54.000Z","msg":"樓上條友真係好撚煩，煩過我條女"},{"pid":"3e42967438ca83e01d0ae6fbbb781655a1366908","tid":460192,"uid":4363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T15:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上條友真係好撚煩，煩過我條女</blockquote><br />\n覺唔覺先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}